data.description: No time to remodel? This home is all ready to go. Fully renovated. Down to studs kitchen and bath remodel, new heat pump, new windows, new roof, new electrical panel/service, new siding, new cedar decks front and back, fully fenced, dog run,  insulated to code (home energy score of 8!), new on demand water heater. So much that you'll never have to do! All appliances included! And don't forget there is a bonus/office space along with two bedrooms and two baths! [Home Energy Score = 8. HES Report at https://rpt.greenbuildingregistry.com/hes/OR10220719]
